Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) da ke karuwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/European Economic Area da United Kingdom, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila wanda ya tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa matakin ya bambanta a kowace ƙasa, annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci, da dakunan kulawa mai tsanani ya kamata su ƙara shirye-shiryen su don karuwar marasa lafiyar COVID-19 waɗanda za su buƙaci kulawar kiwon lafiya, musamman na kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton tarin cututtukan huhu da ba a san asalin su ba a Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa mai haddasa cutar shine sabon coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira coronavirus mai saurin kamuwa da cutar numfashi mai tsanani 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Bayanai da aka samu har zuwa yanzu sun nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 suna fama da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, wato kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan mutanen suna warkewa.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin dari na masu cutar, COVID-19 ta ci gaba zuwa wani yanayi mai tsanani da ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin dari na sauran ke fuskantar rashin lafiya mai tsanani da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke cikin asibiti saboda COVID-19 kusan kashi 4 ne.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika yanayin haɗuwa na COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da United Kingdom (UK) kuma mun kwatanta shi da abubuwan da suka faru a lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a yanzu a ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya kara yaduwa a wurare da dama kuma yanayin annobar COVID-19 a sauran sassan duniya yana bin yanayin annobar a China.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin Eurosurveillance 2020 da aka buga a ranar 5 ga Maris, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton Turai ta farko da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta fara bayar da rahoton mutane uku da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da Ingila (UK), tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da 15 ga Maris, 2020, an samu mutum 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 da aka ruwaito, tare da 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun ƙididdigar tarawa da kuma yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin adadin COVID-19 da kowace ƙasa ke bayarwa a duniya kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe. Ana samun waɗannan adadin ne kawai daga tushen hukuma kamar ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya ta ƙasar, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da WHO.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, da kuma kwatanta shi da yanayin a Italiya.
A matsayin mai nuna alamar yaduwar cutar COVID-19 mai aiki, mun lissafa abubuwan da suka faru na kwanaki 14, don haka muna la'akari da tafiye-tafiye na COVID-19, a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, a cikin lokacin Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin cututtukan da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa har zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da adadin cututtukan da aka ruwaito a Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK
Yanayin haɗuwa da abubuwan da suka faru na kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya suna bin yanayin lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto na 1).
Ga EU/EEA da UK baki ɗaya, yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya ƙaru sosai a kusan ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Ƙarin bayani).
Wannan yanayin ya kasance ne saboda saurin karuwar adadin masu cutar da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya suna nuna irin wannan yanayin karuwar abubuwan da ke faruwa na COVID-19 (Ƙarin bayani).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK idan aka kwatanta da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Bayanai sun nuna cewa, har zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun ba da rahoton jimlar adadin masu cutar da ya yi daidai da jimlar adadin Italiya makonni uku da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 da aka ruwaito suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da UK.
Yanayin da aka lura a cikin abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ƙaruwa a cikin daidaitattun ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da bambancin matakan da ƙasashe ke fuskanta, bambancin amsar lafiyar jama'a, da yiwuwar bambancin ma'anar shari'ar tsakanin ƙasashe da bambancin ladabi don zaɓar marasa lafiya da za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, wanda ya haɗa da gwajin biyo baya.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan Italiya da abin ya shafa sun bayyana halin da ake ciki na kimanin kashi 10% na marasa lafiyar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da raka'a kulawa mai tsanani a yankin sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
A halin yanzu, ana samun bayanai ne kawai game da karɓar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na masu cutar (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Koyaya, dole ne a tattara bayanan ta hanyar da ta dace don haɓaka bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan adadin rahotannin da aka bayar da kuma yawan mutuwar.
Nazarin da aka gudanar a 2010-2011 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin wadatar gadaje masu kulawa da kulawa a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a kowace 100,000 na yawan a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 gadaje na kulawa da kulawa da kulawa da 100,000 a cikin 2010-2011).
Yanayin samfurin da ya shafi yawan lafiyar lafiya, tare da kimanta yawan adadin COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti ga kowace EU/EEA da UK da ke da alaƙa da haɗarin >90% ya wuce ƙarfin gado mai kulawa, an bayar da shi a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ƙimar haɗarin ECDC mai sauri akan COVID-19.
Saboda har zuwa yanzu an tattara adadin cututtukan a cikin wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da UK, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da hankali galibi suna kula da wasu yankuna na yanki na yanki, ya kamata a samar da bayanai game da shari'o'i da gadajen kulawa da hankali a matakin Sunan Yankin Yankin 2 don Kididdiga (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Saboda haka, jihohi, asibitoci, da dakunan kulawa da gaggawa ya kamata su shirya don yanayin watsawa na SARS-CoV-2 da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiyar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawar kiwon lafiya, musamman a cikin kulawa mai tsanani, kamar yadda ya faru a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon kimantawa na haɗarin ECDC, hanzari, aiki, da kuma cikakkiyar hanya suna da mahimmanci don rage saurin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, tare da sauyawa daga tsarin hanawa zuwa tsarin ragewa, saboda saurin karuwar adadin lokuta, kamar yadda aka zata, na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa, da daidaitawa da amsawa idan ba a aiwatar da su ba a baya.
Har ila yau, wannan saurin kimanta haɗarin ya ƙunshi matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai gajeren lokacin dama yayin da ƙasashe ke da damar ƙara haɓaka ƙoƙarin sarrafawa don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan hakan ta gaza, sauran tsarin kiwon lafiya na EU/EEA na iya fuskantar hauhawar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ke haifar da cutar sankarar barkwanci mai saurin kamuwa da cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ya zuwa yanzu ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'i ga bil'adama.
Kamar kwayar cutar ta SARS-CoV, wacce ta haifar da SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mai yaduwa daga bat kuma yana haifar da irin wannan alamun ta hanyar irin wannan hanyar.
Ko da yake, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan cututtuka da mutuwar fiye da SARS, amma yana da saurin yaduwa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa, kuma yana shafar maza fiye da mata.
