Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, kasar Sin, kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a duk fadin kasar da kuma kusan kasashe 50 a duniya.
Har zuwa 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da tabbatar da shari'o'in COVID-19 80,000, tare da dawo da marasa lafiya 40,000 da mutuwar marasa lafiya 3,000.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine "magabcin jama'a na 1" kuma yana da yuwuwar yin lahani fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu tun lokacin da aka fara rahoton a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020 wanda ya kafa jerin ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ware daga wasu marasa lafiya, an buga takardu sama da 200 game da COVID-19, wanda ya haɗa da ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, cututtukan cututtuka, ilimin halittar cuta, ganewar asali, da magani.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙarin taƙaita ci gaban bincike a cikin wannan sabon fannin da ke haɓaka cikin sauri.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wata cuta da wasu CVD ke haifarwa, wato, cutar murar Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, barkewar cutar a shekarar 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da rigakafi da kuma tsinkayar cututtuka da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci da ba a amsa ba.
A al'adance, ana ɗaukar CoVs a matsayin ƙwayoyin cuta marasa lahani ga mutane, musamman suna haifar da kusan kashi 15% na mura 4.
Duk da haka, a wannan karni, mun sami CoVs biyu masu cutarwa ga mutane, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, kowannensu ya haifar da barkewar cutar da ta fara a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, kuma nan da nan ta bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan rashin lafiya da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 a halin yanzu shine barkewar CoV na uku a tarihin ɗan adam.
