Glycoprotein mai ƙwanƙwasawa ko spike (S) yana ɗaure da mai karɓar kwayoyin halitta, angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE 2) da dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) don SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, sannan haɗuwa da membrane yana faruwa.
Ana sakin kwayoyin RNA na kwayar cutar zuwa cikin cytoplasm; bayan kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar, RNA na genomic tare da glycoproteins da nucleocapsid sun hada da vesicles dauke da virions, wanda daga bisani ya haɗu da membrane plasma don saki kwayar cutar.
An fara rahoton jerin kwayoyin SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 10 ga Janairu, 2020.
SARS-CoV-2 wani sabon nau'in beta-CoV ne wanda ke da kamanceceniya ta kwayoyin halitta sama da kashi 99.98% tsakanin samfuran 10 da aka tsara; an samo samfurin ne daga asalin barkewar cutar, Kasuwar Abinci ta Kifi ta Huanan a Wuhan.
A cikin kwayoyin halitta, SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kama da SARS-CoV fiye da MERS-CoV.
Ta hanyar amfani da na'urar daukar hotan lantarki, an gano kwayoyin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin wani sashi na ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta na mutum.
An gano ACE2 na ɗan adam a matsayin mai karɓar SARS-CoV-2 kamar SARS-CoV.
Koyaya, furotin S na SARS-CoV-2 yana ɗaure da ACE2 na ɗan adam da rauni fiye da yadda yake ɗaure da furotin S na SARS-CoV, wanda ya dace da gaskiyar cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da kamuwa da cuta wanda ba shi da tsanani kamar kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV a cikin marasa lafiya.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya kuma samar da sabbin ƙwayoyin cuta masu gajeren lokaci waɗanda aka ɓoye tare da orf3b da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ɓoye tare da code orf8.
Furotin orf3b na SARS-CoV-2 na iya taka rawa wajen cutar kwayar cutar da kuma hana bayyanar IFNβ; duk da haka, orf8 ba shi da wani yanki na aiki ko dalili.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Zhou, et al. sun ba da rahoton cikakken tsarin cryo-EM na mutum ACE2 a ƙuduri na 2.9 Å a cikin hadaddun tare da jigilar amino acid B0AT1.
Sun gano cewa hadaddun, waɗanda ke da buɗe da rufe ƙirar, an haɗa su don samar da dimer kuma ACE2-B0AT1 hadaddun na iya ɗaure sunadarai biyu na S, wanda ke da hujja don ganowa da kamuwa da cutar CoV.
B0AT1 na iya zama maƙasudin magani a cikin tace magunguna don hana kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2.
