Sau da yawa zazzabi ne babban alamun COVID-19 da farkonsa, tare da ko ba tare da wasu alamun bayyanar cututtuka kamar bushewar tari, numfashi, ciwon tsoka, ƙuƙwalwa, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, rhinorrhea, ciwon kirji, zawo, tashin zuciya, da amai ba.
Wasu marasa lafiya suna fama da dyspnea da/ko hypoxaemia mako guda bayan farawar cutar.
A cikin mawuyacin hali, ci gaban cutar mai haƙuri yana ci gaba da sauri zuwa cututtukan numfashi, septic shock, acidosis na metabolic, da coagulopathy.
Marasa lafiya da ke fama da zazzabi da / ko bayyanar cututtuka na numfashi da zazzabi mai tsanani, koda kuwa ba tare da cutar hoto ba, ya kamata a bincika su don cutar don ganewar asali.
Nazarin alƙaluma a ƙarshen Disamba 2019 ya nuna cewa kashi 98% na alamun cutar zazzabi ne, kashi 76% na tari mai bushe, kashi 55% na numfashi, da kashi 3% na zawo; 8% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar tallafin iska.
An bayar da rahoton irin wannan binciken a cikin binciken biyu na kwanan nan, nazarin iyali da kuma tarin da ke haifar da watsawa daga mutane masu asymptomatic.
A kwatankwacin haka, nazarin alƙaluma a cikin 2012 ya nuna cewa marasa lafiya na MERS-CoV suna da zazzabi (98%), tari mai bushewa (47%), da numfashi (55%) a matsayin manyan alamun.
Duk da haka, kashi 80% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar tallafin iska, fiye da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kuma ya dace da mafi girman mutuwar MERS fiye da COVID-19.
Diarrhea (26%) da ciwon makogwaro (21%) an kuma lura da su a cikin marasa lafiya na MERS.
A cikin marasa lafiya na SARS, zazzabi (99%-100%), bushewar tari (29%-75%), dyspnea (40%-42%), zawo (20-25%), da ciwon makogwaro (13-25%) an nuna su a matsayin manyan alamun bayyanar cututtuka kuma ana buƙatar tallafin iska a kusan 14%-20% na marasa lafiya.
