Saboda rashin gogewa tare da sabon CoV, likitoci galibi suna ba da kulawa ta tallafi ga marasa lafiyar COVID-19, yayin da suke gwada magungunan da aka yi amfani da su ko aka ba da shawarar a baya don maganin sauran CoVs, kamar SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, da sauran cututtukan kwayar cuta (Table 2).2).2.
Wannan ya hada da maganin da ake da shi yanzu da kuma yiwuwar maganin da kwayoyin rigakafi, masu hana rigakafi, steroids, jini daga marasa lafiya da suka warke, maganin gargajiya na kasar Sin, da kuma tallafin tunani.
Har ma an ba da shawarar yin amfani da jini na marasa lafiya da suka warke don warkar da su.
Kamfanonin harhada magunguna suna neman samar da rigakafi da allurar rigakafi ga cutar.
A farkon matakin, SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kaiwa garkuwar jiki hari kuma yana iya kaiwa wasu gabobin da ke bayyana ACE2 a ƙananan matakan, kamar tsarin hanji da kodan.
Amma, rashin aiki da kuma rashin numfashi suna da haɗari ga marasa lafiya kuma su ne manyan sanadin mutuwa.
Saboda haka, tallafin numfashi yana da mahimmanci don sauƙaƙe alamun cututtuka da ceton rayuka, wanda ya haɗa da maganin oxygen na yau da kullun, oxygen mai gudana, iska mai ƙarancin iska, da kuma iska mai ƙarfi, dangane da tsananin cutar.
Masu haƙuri da ke fama da matsanancin numfashi dole ne a tallafa musu da ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta ta ECMO, wanda shine hanyar da ake amfani da ita don magance ciwon zuciya ko numfashi mai haɗari.
Bugu da kari, kula da daidaiton wutan lantarki, rigakafi da kula da kamuwa da cuta ta biyu da harin septic, da kuma kare ayyukan gabobin rayuwa ma suna da mahimmanci ga marasa lafiya na SARS-CoV-2.
An san cewa mummunan halayen tsarin garkuwar jiki yana haifar da guguwar cytokine a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS da MERS.
Cytokine Storm wani nau'i ne na tsarin kumburi wanda aka nuna ta hanyar sakin jerin cytokines, wanda ya hada da TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, da MCP-1.
Wadannan cytokines suna haifar da kwayoyin cuta don saki yawancin 'yancin radicals wanda shine babban dalilin ARDS da rashin cin nasara.
