Koyaya, steroids a manyan allurai ba su da amfani ga mummunan raunin huhu a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS da COVID-19.
A akasin wannan, steroids na iya haifar da mummunan sakamako, musamman osteonecrosis, wanda ke shafar hangen nesa.
