Daga baya, remdesivir ya nuna hanawa ga wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA guda ɗaya, waɗanda suka haɗa da MERS da SARS.
Bisa ga wannan, Gilead ta samar da wannan fili ga China don gudanar da jerin gwaje-gwaje a kan mutanen da ke da cutar SARS-CoV-2, kuma sakamakon yana da matukar muhimmanci.
