An yi amfani da TCM don magance cututtuka daban-daban a China tsawon dubban shekaru.
Duk da haka, tasirinsa ya dogara ne da yawancin abubuwan da ke cikin tsari.
Yawancin abubuwan da ke da tasiri ba a san su ba ko kuma ba a bayyana su ba saboda yana da wuya a cire ko tabbatar da waɗannan abubuwan ko kuma mafi kyawun haɗuwa.
A halin yanzu, saboda babu ingantaccen magani na musamman don COVID-19, TCM ya zama ɗayan manyan magunguna masu madadin marasa lafiya tare da alamun rashin lafiya mai sauƙi zuwa matsakaici ko kuma waɗanda ke murmurewa daga mummunan cuta.
Misali, an gano cewa Shu Feng Jie Du da Lian Hua Qing Wen sun yi tasiri wajen maganin COVID-19.
An lura da mafi girman adadin warkewa a cikin maganin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a lardunan China da ke amfani da TCM a cikin kashi 87% na marasa lafiya, wanda ya haɗa da Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), da Hunan (50%), yayin da lardin Hubei, wanda ke amfani da TCM a cikin kusan 30% na marasa lafiyar COVID-19, yana da mafi ƙarancin adadin warkewa (13%).
Duk da haka, wannan kwatanta har yanzu yana da matukar damuwa saboda yawancin sauran abubuwan da ke shafar, kamar yawan marasa lafiya da kuma tsanani, dole ne a haɗa su cikin kimantawa.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Boli Zhang da abokan aikinsa sun buga wani bincike da ya kwatanta maganin maganin Yammacin Turai (WM) da maganin haɗin gwiwa na WM da TCM.
Sun gano cewa lokacin da ake bukata don dawo da zafin jiki, bayyanar cututtuka, da kuma asibiti ya fi guntu a cikin ƙungiyar WM + TCM fiye da ƙungiyar WM kadai.
Abin da ya fi ban sha'awa, ƙimar lalacewar bayyanar cututtuka (daga mai sauƙi zuwa mai tsanani) ya fi ƙasa da ƙungiyar WM+TCM fiye da ƙungiyar WM kawai (7.4% vs 46.2%) da kuma ƙananan mutuwar a cikin ƙungiyar WM+TCM fiye da ƙungiyar WM kawai (8.8% vs 39%).
Koyaya, inganci da amincin TCM har yanzu suna jiran gwaji mafi kyau a kan manyan sikelin da kuma a cikin ƙarin cibiyoyin bincike.
Wani abu mai ban sha'awa shine a bayyana yadda ake aiki da kuma bayyana abubuwan da ke da tasiri a cikin maganin TCM ko haɗuwa da su, idan ya yiwu.
Yawancin marasa lafiya da ake zargi ko tabbatar da su da COVID-19 suna jin tsoron wannan cuta mai saurin yaduwa da kisa, kuma mutanen da ke keɓewa suna jin gundura, kaɗaici, da fushi.
