An tsara dabarun allurar rigakafi don MERS ta amfani da ƙwayoyin cuta, DNA plasmids, masu ɗaukar hoto, nanoparticles, ƙwayoyin cuta masu kama da ƙwayoyin cuta, da ƙwayoyin cuta masu haɗuwa kuma an kimanta su a cikin dabbobi.
Samar da allurar rigakafi mai lafiya da tasiri ga mutanen da ba su da rigakafi ga SARS-CoV-2 aiki ne mai matukar muhimmanci da kuma gaggawa don sarrafa annobar da ke gudana.
