A yawancin lokuta, marasa lafiya suna iya warkewa ba tare da ciwo ba.
Koyaya, kamar SARS da MERS, COVID-19 kuma yana da alaƙa da yawan rashin lafiya da mutuwa a cikin marasa lafiya masu fama da cutar.
