Amfani da steroid: Kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, steroids sune magungunan rigakafi wanda aka yi amfani da su sosai a matsayin maganin tallafi don cututtukan cututtuka don rage tsananin lalacewar kumburi.
Saboda ana amfani da magungunan corticosteroids masu yawa a cikin marasa lafiya masu fama da cutar SARS, yawancin waɗanda suka tsira daga cutar sun ƙare da cutar osteonecrosis avascular tare da nakasa na rayuwa da ƙarancin rayuwa.
Saboda haka, idan ya cancanta, ya kamata a yi amfani da steroids a ƙananan allurai da gajeren lokaci a cikin marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
Matsin lamba: Kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, a lokacin barkewar COVID-19, yawancin marasa lafiya suna fama da matsanancin damuwa saboda dole ne su shiga cikin keɓewa na dogon lokaci da rashin tabbas mai tsanani da kuma ganin mutuwar dangin dangi da sauran marasa lafiya.
