Koyaya, a ranar 19 ga Janairun 2020, darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Wuhan ya kwantar da hankalin jama'a ta hanyar cewa sabon kwayar cutar tana da ƙarancin yaduwa da iyakantaccen damar haifuwa daga mutum zuwa mutum kuma rigakafi da hana cutar ba matsala bane.
Wannan sakon ya kwantar da hankalin jama'a, musamman ma a lokacin da ake shirin bikin bazara a kasar, saboda haka lokaci mai muhimmanci ya yi latti don dakile cutar a Wuhan.
Hukumar kula da cututtuka a ƙasar Sin za ta iya koyon darasi daga wannan kuma ta yi gyara mai girma a nan gaba.
Misali, ya kamata su (1) yi taka tsantsan wajen yin sanarwa ga jama'a domin duk wata kalma da za su fada za ta iya shafar halin da suke ciki da kuma yanke shawara; (2) su kasance masu saukin kai da kuma amsawa ga bayanan da ba na yau da kullun ba daga asibiti maimakon jiran rahoton likita ko jami'in da ya cancanta; (3) su kasance masu taka tsantsan don dakile yiwuwar barkewar cutar a farkon matakin, maimakon kokarin kwantar da hankalin jama'a; da kuma (4) su fi yawan fitar da atisaye masu tasiri da tasiri don wayar da kan jama'a game da barkewar cutar da kuma gwadawa da inganta tsarin amsawar jama'a akai-akai.
Cutar COVID-19 ta barke ne sakamakon sabon kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 wanda ya fara yaduwa a ƙarshen Disamba 2019.
A cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, annobar ta bazu ko'ina cikin China da ƙasashe sama da 50 a duniya a lokacin rubuta wannan bita.
Saboda kwayar cutar ta yi kama da SARS-CoV kuma alamun COVID-19 da SARS sun yi kama, barkewar COVID-19 ta zama kamar barkewar SARS.
Koyaya, akwai wasu bambance-bambance masu mahimmanci tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS, waɗanda ke da mahimmanci don hana yaduwar cutar da kula da marasa lafiya.
COVID-19 ta fi shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma ta fi shafar maza fiye da mata, kuma yawan mutuwar ma ya fi girma a cikin tsofaffi fiye da matasa.
Mutuwar SARS ta fi ta COVID-19 (10.91% zuwa 1.44%).
Marasa lafiya na COVID-19 suna watsa kwayar cutar koda kuwa basu da alamomi, yayin da marasa lafiya na SARS galibi suna watsa kwayar cutar yayin da suke cikin mawuyacin hali. Wannan yana haifar da matsala mafi girma wajen hana yaduwar COVID-19 fiye da SARS.
Wannan ya bayyana wani ɓangare na dalilin da yasa SARS-CoV-2 ke yaduwa da sauri kuma ya fi SARS-CoV yawa.
Ana iya yin gwajin RNA na yau da kullun don bincika SARS-CoV-2 don samun sakamako mara kyau a wasu marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
A gefe guda kuma, marasa lafiya da suka warke suna iya sake samun tabbatacce a gwajin cutar.
Wannan binciken ya kara hadarin yaduwar cutar.
Tare da saurin ci gaban binciken COVID-19, wasu mahimman batutuwa har yanzu ba a warware su ba, kamar:
