Kwayar cutar corona (CoV) ta fito ne daga dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya kunshi rukuni na kwayar cutar RNA mai laushi, mai laushi, da kuma guda ɗaya.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana da mafi girman kwayoyin halitta a cikin girman kilobases 26 zuwa 32 a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA da ake kira "CoV", saboda siffar da ke kama da kambi a ƙarƙashin microscope na lantarki.
Bisa ga tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halitta marasa rarrabuwa waɗanda ke da tsari iri ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu cikin uku na kwayoyin halitta sun ƙunshi manyan sassan karatu guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b) waɗanda ke kan juna.
Polyproteins suna ci gaba da sarrafawa don samar da sunadarai 16 marasa tsari, wanda ake kira nsp1~16.
Sauran kwayoyin halitta sun ƙunshi ƙirar buɗewa (ORF) don furotin na tsarin, wanda ya haɗa da ƙuƙwalwa ko spike (S), shell ko envelope (E), membrane (M), da nucleoprotein (N).
Wasu ƙwayoyin cuta masu dacewa da keɓaɓɓu ga wasu ƙwayoyin cuta suna kuma ɓoye ta hanyar ƙwayoyin cuta daban-daban na CoV.
Dangane da bambance-bambance a cikin jerin sunayen furotin, an rarraba CoVs zuwa jinsuna huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, da delta-CoV); daga cikin waɗannan jinsuna huɗu, beta-CoVs suna da mafi yawan HCoVs kuma an sake rarraba su zuwa layin zuriya huɗu (A, B, C, da D).
Shaidar phylogenetic ta nuna cewa bat da rodents sune tushen asalin alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da kaji shine babban ma'ajiyar gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoVs sun ci gaba da ƙetare shingen jinsuna kuma wasu CoVs sun zama manyan cututtukan cututtuka a cikin mutane.
A halin yanzu, an san mutane bakwai da ke dauke da kwayar cutar HCoV.
Daga cikin waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta bakwai, HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alpha-CoVs.
