Sabuwar HCoV ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda yanzu ake kira SARS-CoV-2, ita ce mai haifar da annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ta kashe mutane sama da 3,120 kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 91,000 har zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020.
