Ana iya gano farkon cutar SARS a ƙarshen 2002 a lardin Guangdong, China.
Cutar ta SARS ta haifar da rahotanni 8,096 tare da mutuwar 774, wanda ya bazu a ƙasashe da nahiyoyi da yawa.
Baya ga masu saurin kamuwa da cuta, ana tsammanin kowane lamari zai haifar da kusan lambobi biyu na biyu, tare da lokacin incubation na kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 kuma ana ganin ƙimar nauyin kwayar cutar a ranar 10 na cutar.
