Ana ba da rahoton cewa masu sayayya suna tara kayayyaki saboda tsoron COVID-19 idan jama'a suka keɓe kansu.
A ranar Laraba, Woolworths kuma ya iyakance sayen buhunan bayan gida don aikawa gida zuwa fakiti ɗaya a kowane tsari.
