Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana barkewar cutar COVID-19 da ke faruwa cuta da kwayar cutar coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin annoba.
Duk da cewa kalmar "annoba" tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu ne kawai, ba yadda cutar take da haɗari ba, WHO ta lura da buƙatar ƙarfafa gwamnatoci su ɗauki mataki:
Dukkan ƙasashe na iya canza yanayin wannan annoba.
Idan kasashe suka gano, gwada, magance, ware, da kuma tattara jama'arsu don amsawa, in ji Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Darakta Janar na WHO.
Muna cikin matukar damuwa saboda yawan yaduwar cutar da kuma yadda take da tsanani da kuma jinkirin da ake samu.
In ji Dokta Tom Frieden, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amirka, annobar "ba ta taɓa faruwa ba".
Ya ce, a wani bayanin da aka wallafa a CNN a watan Fabrairu, "ban da mura, babu wata kwayar cuta ta numfashi da aka taɓa gano daga fitowarta zuwa ci gaba da yaduwa a duniya".
Ghebreyesus ya bayyana irin wannan ra'ayi, yana cewa "ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da cutar coronavirus ta haifar ba".
Ya ci gaba, "kuma ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da za a iya sarrafa ta a lokaci guda ba".
Sabon matsayin annobar ya biyo bayan shawarar WHO a watan Janairu da ta ayyana cutar a matsayin gagarumin matsalar lafiyar jama'a da ke damun duniya.
Darakta na Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amirka, Dokta Anthony Fauci, ya ce game da annobar, "ainihin, za ta yi muni".
Har zuwa ranar Alhamis, Associated Press ta ruwaito akwai aƙalla mutane 126,000 da suka kamu da COVID-19 a duk duniya, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane sama da 4,600.
Cutar annobar coronavirus ta 2019-2020 annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) ce da ke gudana kuma ta haifar da cutar coronavirus mai saurin kamuwa da cutar numfashi ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
An gano barkewar cutar a Wuhan, China, a watan Disamba na 2019, an ayyana ta a matsayin gagarumar matsalar lafiyar jama'a a duniya a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma an ayyana ta a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
Har zuwa 10 ga Afrilu 2020, an samu kusan mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kasashe 210 da yankuna, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 97,000.
Mutane 364,000 ne suka warke.
