Hakanan an shafi jadawalin jirage kuma an canza su.Koriya ta Kudu ta gabatar da abin da ake ganin shine mafi girma kuma mafi kyawun tsari a duniya don tace cutar a cikin yawan jama'a, ware duk wanda ya kamu da cutar, da kuma bin diddigin da ke kewaye da su.
