Manufofin magance annoba sun haɗa da rage yaduwar cutar tsakanin ma'aikata, kare mutanen da ke da haɗarin kamuwa da cututtukan rashin lafiya, ci gaba da ayyukan kasuwanci, da rage tasirin cutar ga sauran ƙungiyoyi a cikin sarkar samarwa.
