b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne wanda yake kan farfajiyar waje na sel (ƙwayoyin sel) a cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ACE2 yana da aikin da ya saba wa enzymes masu canza angiotensin (ACE), ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin-II da haɓaka Angiotensin (1-7), yana mai da shi kyakkyawan maƙasudin magani don magance cututtukan zuciya.
Ana kiran ɗan adam ACE2 sau da yawa a matsayin hACE2.
Angiotensin mai juyawa 2 shine zinc-mai dauke da sinadarin zinc wanda yake a saman endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Kwayar ACE2 tana da yankin M2 peptidase-N-terminal da kuma yankin jigilar amino acid na renal collectrin-C-terminal.
ACE2 shine nau'in furotin membrane mai nau'in nau'i na I, tare da ƙwayoyin halitta masu aiki a kan ƙwayoyin halitta a cikin huhu da sauran kyallen takarda.
Ana raba yankin ACE2 na waje daga yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme, wanda aka sani da sheddase, kuma ana sakin furotin da aka narkar da shi zuwa jini kuma a ƙarshe ana fitar dashi cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin mafi yawan gabobin jiki: ACE2 yana haɗe da ƙwayoyin halitta musamman ƙwayoyin alveolar huhu na nau'in II, ƙananan ƙwayoyin intestinal, ƙwayoyin endothelial na arteries da veins, da ƙwayoyin tsoka mai sauƙi a cikin mafi yawan gabobin jiki.
Ana kuma gano bayanin mRNA ACE2 a cikin ƙwayar kwakwalwa, striatum, hypothalamus, da kuma kwakwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine daidaita ACE.
ACE yana karya hormone angiotensin I zuwa angiotensin II wanda yake haifar da ƙwayoyin cuta.
A ƙarshe, ACE2 ya yanke amino acid phenylalanine na ƙarshen carboxyl daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma ya yi hydrolysis zuwa angiotensin (1-7) mai karɓar jini (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma yana iya karya wasu peptides da suka hada da [des-Arg9] -bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana tsara zirga-zirgar membrane na mai jigilar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19 kuma yana da hannu cikin cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai watsawa, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban hanyar shiga cikin sel don wasu coronaviruses, waɗanda suka haɗa da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, ɗaurewar sunadarai na S1 a cikin SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 spikes ko bulges tare da yankin enzymatic ACE2 a farfajiyar sel yana haifar da endocytosis da fassarar kwayar cutar da enzymes zuwa cikin endosomes da ke cikin sel.
Wannan hanyar shigar da kwayar cutar ta kuma buƙaci priming S-protein ta hanyar mai karɓar serine protease TMPRSS2, wanda hana shi ake bincika a halin yanzu a matsayin magani mai yuwuwa.
Duk da haka, yawancin ƙungiyoyi masu sana'a da hukumomi suna ba da shawarar ci gaba da maganin ACE inhibitor da ARB na yau da kullun.
Wani bita da bincike mai zurfi, wanda aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012, ya gano cewa "amfani da masu hana ACE yana haifar da raguwa mai yawa na 34% a hadarin ciwon huhu idan aka kwatanta da iko".
Bugu da ƙari, "amfani da masu hana ACE yana rage haɗarin ciwon huhu a cikin marasa lafiya waɗanda ke da haɗarin ciwon huhu, musamman marasa lafiya da ke fama da bugun jini da rashin ƙarfi.
Yin amfani da ACE inhibitors kuma an danganta shi da rage yawan mutuwar da ke da nasaba da ciwon huhu, ko da yake sakamakon bai da ƙarfi idan aka kwatanta da haɗarin ciwon huhu gaba ɗaya".
Abubuwan da ke tattare da mutum na mutum (rhACE2) ana sa ran zama sabon magani don raunin huhu, kuma yana nuna yana haɓaka haemodynamics na huhu da kuma wadatar oxygen a cikin 'yan alade tare da cutar ta acute respiratory syndrome wanda aka haifar da lipoplysarid.
Lokacin rabi na rhACE2 a cikin mutane shine kimanin sa'o'i 10 tare da farawa na aiki na minti 30 ban da tsawon lokacin sakamako na sa'o'i 24.
Wasu binciken sun nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama magani mai ban sha'awa ga marasa lafiya tare da rashin haƙuri ga masu hana tsarin renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) na gargajiya ko kuma a cikin cututtukan da angiotensin II ke cikin jini.
b'Aikace-aikacen COVID-19 aikace-aikacen software ne na wayar hannu wanda aka tsara don taimakawa bin diddigin lamba don magance cutar coronavirus ta 2019-2020, wanda shine tsarin gano mutane ("masu lamba") waɗanda wataƙila sun yi hulɗa da mutanen da ke da cutar.
Yawancin aikace-aikace da aka haɓaka ko aka gabatar, waɗanda ke da tallafi na hukuma a wasu yankuna da hukunce-hukuncen.
An samar da wasu tsarin don gina aikace-aikacen bin diddigin lamba.
Batutuwan sirri sun kasance masu tambaya, musamman dangane da tsarin da ya dogara da bin diddigin wurin da masu amfani da aikace-aikacen suke.
Sauran hanyoyin da ba su da matsala game da sirrin sirri sun haɗa da amfani da siginar Bluetooth don lura da kusanci da mai amfani da wasu wayoyin hannu.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Google da Apple sun sanar cewa za su haɗa ayyukan don tallafawa waɗannan ƙa'idodin tushen Bluetooth kai tsaye cikin tsarin aiki na Android da iOS.
A China, gwamnatin kasar Sin, tare da Alipay, sun kaddamar da wata manhaja da ke ba 'yan ƙasa damar bincika ko sun taɓa yin hulɗa da masu cutar COVID-19.
Ana amfani da wannan manhajar a birane sama da 200 na kasar Sin.
An kirkiro wannan aikace-aikacen ne ta hanyar al'ummar IT ta gida, an saki shi a matsayin tushen budewa kuma za a mika shi ga gwamnati.
Ma'aikatar Sadarwa da Fasaha da Ma'aikatar Lafiya ne suka samar da wannan manhajar.
Har zuwa 14 ga Afrilu 2020, aikace-aikacen har yanzu suna jiran amincewar Google Play Store da Apple App Store.
A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, gwamnati ta bayyana cewa aikace-aikacen bin diddigin lamba yana cikin ci gaba da ci gaba kuma zai kasance a shirye don rarrabawa a cikin 'yan makonni.
Australia da New Zealand suna la'akari da aikace-aikacen da ke kan aikace-aikacen TraceTogether na Singapore da yarjejeniyar BlueTrace. Rasha na niyyar gabatar da aikace-aikacen geofencing don marasa lafiya da aka gano da COVID-19 da ke zaune a Moscow; an tsara wannan aikace-aikacen don tabbatar da cewa ba su bar gida ba.
Ross Anderson, farfesa a fannin injiniyan tsaro a Jami'ar Cambridge, ya ambaci wasu matsaloli masu amfani da za su iya faruwa a tsarin da ke amfani da aikace-aikace, wanda ya hada da tabbataccen karya da yiwuwar rashin tasiri idan bayanan da aikace-aikacen ya dauka ya iyakance ga karamin yanki na yawan jama'a.
Don magance damuwa game da yaduwar aikace-aikacen "coronavirus" masu ɓatarwa ko cutarwa, Apple ya sanya iyaka kan nau'ikan ƙungiyoyi waɗanda za su iya ƙara aikace-aikacen da ke da alaƙa da coronavirus zuwa App Store, ƙuntatawa kawai ga ƙungiyoyi "hukuma" ko masu suna.
Google da Amazon suna da irin wannan ƙuntatawa.
Masu ba da shawara game da sirri sun nuna damuwarsu game da tasirin sa ido kan jama'a ta amfani da aikace-aikacen coronavirus, musamman game da ko za a dakatar da tsarin sa ido da aka gina don magance cutar coronavirus bayan barazanar ta wuce.
Amnesty International da kuma wasu kungiyoyi sama da 100 sun fitar da wata sanarwa da ke kira da a takaita irin wannan sa ido.
